V0420_01_00_00_0.text:
Sure!
I'm gonna win this Duel with a TKO!

V0420_01_00_01_0.text: Step into the ring and we'll go mano-a-mano!

V0420_01_00_02_0.text:
Dueling is my life!
Let's do this!

V0420_01_00_03_0.text:
I've been hungering to Duel ya!
Don't let me down!

V0420_01_00_04_0.text: I'm giving my all in this Duel, so you better too!

V0420_01_00_05_0.text: Yuma, let's make this the most epic battle ever!

V0420_01_00_06_0.text:
Yuma! Astral!
This is one fight that you can't win!

V0420_01_00_07_0.text: I wanna beat the best by playing my best!

V0420_01_00_07_1.text:
Let's Duel, Yuma!
You too, Astral!

V0420_01_00_08_0.text:
No tricks, Girag!
Just a straight fight to the finish!

V0420_01_00_09_0.text:
Don Thousand...
I'm gonna end you!

V0420_03_00_00_0.text: Ready to throw in the towel?

V0420_03_00_01_0.text: Let's keep playing to the final card!

V0420_03_00_03_0.text: A small jab will put me in position to win.

V0420_03_00_05_0.text: I've taken bigger hits than this before!

V0420_05_00_00_0.text: If that's how you're gonna fight, I won't hold back!

V0420_06_01_01_0.text: That's what I was waiting for!

V0420_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0420_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0420_16_00_01_0.text: You're going down for the ten count!

V0420_21_00_00_1.text: Can't wait to see what you try!

V0420_21_00_01_0.text:
Having fun?
Or are my elite skills spoiling the Duel for ya?

V0420_21_00_02_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0420_21_00_04_0.text: I can sense this Duel is about to get even more intense!

V0420_28_00_00_0.text:
I'm Alito!
The one name you'll never forget!

V0420_28_00_01_0.text:
Hahaha!
This was the kind of Duel I was hoping for!

V0420_28_00_02_0.text:
How's that!
When I'm on my game, I'm unstoppable!

V0420_28_00_03_0.text:
That was fun!
Ready for round two?

V0420_28_00_04_0.text: I could tell just how badly you wanted to win, Yuma!

V0420_28_00_04_1.text: That's what made this Duel worth Dueling!

V0420_28_00_05_0.text: While you keep failing, I get it done!

V0420_28_00_06_0.text:
There's no one I can't knock out!
Get outta my sight!

V0420_29_00_00_0.text:
Sigh...
My counter tactics didn't work at all.

V0420_29_00_01_0.text:
Heh...
I'm glad I got to Duel ya.

V0420_29_00_02_0.text:
Remember my name!
Cuz I'm your rival for life!

V0420_29_00_04_0.text:
Yuma, Astral...
I hope you had as much fun as I did.

V0420_29_00_06_0.text: That's why you're my best bud, Girag!

V0420_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show ya just what I can do!

V0420_43_00_00_1.text: I've been taking it easy on you - but not anymore!

V0420_30_00_00_0.text: Start by turning up the heat.

V0420_30_00_01_0.text: Use the unexpected to catch 'em off guard.

V0420_30_00_02_0.text: I'll play it cool before unleashing my most disarming line.

V0420_34_00_00_0.text: I'll keep all my focus on Dueling!

V0420_34_00_01_0.text: I’m not gonna get distracted like you!

V0420_34_00_03_0.text: Do you believe “love at first sight” is real?

V0420_34_00_04_0.text: What you're doing isn't Dueling! Get outta here!

V0420_34_00_05_0.text: If you won't attack me, I can't counter you!

V0420_34_00_07_0.text: This is the type of Duel I wanted!

V0420_35_00_00_0.text: One thing I'll always have is Dueling!

V0420_35_00_01_0.text: The name's Alito - don't you forget it!

V0420_36_00_02_0.text: This is your chance to counter 'em!

V0420_36_00_06_0.text:
Fine.
I'll let you play, Girag.

V0420_36_00_08_0.text: Can't make a comeback if we don't get into trouble first!

V0420_26_00_01_0.text: You need to do better than that!

V0420_08_00_01_0.text: With this card, I'll knock ya out of the ring!

V0420_08_00_02_0.text:
Here I go!
Barian's Chaos Draw!

V0420_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Barian Untopia!

V0420_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Seventh Ascension!

V0420_08_00_06_0.text: I discard a Rank-Up-Magic to use Seventh Ascension's effect!

V0420_08_00_06_1.text: This card gains that Rank-Up-Magic's effect!

V0420_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Battlin' Boxing Spirits!

V0420_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Reload!

V0420_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rebirth of the Seventh Emperors!

V0420_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Reincarnation of the Seventh Emperors!

V0420_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Seventh Eternity!

V0420_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Jolt Counter!

V0420_08_00_14_0.text:
I have a Counter Trap ready!
I activate Last Counter!

V0420_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Xyz Block!

V0420_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Numbers Overlay Boost!

V0420_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Blast with Chain!

V0420_08_00_18_0.text: Blast with Chain activates when it's destroyed by an effect!

V0420_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Face-Off!

V0420_08_00_20_0.text: I activate Showdown of the Secret Sense Scroll Techniques!

V0420_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Forced Back!

V0420_08_00_22_1.text: I activate my Counter Trap, Counter Counter!

V0420_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Chivalry!

V0420_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Destruction Punch!

V0420_08_00_25_0.text:
I play my Continuous Spell!
Continuous Destruction Punch!

V0420_08_00_26_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Lucky Punch!

V0420_39_00_00_0.text:
Nice!
I get to draw cards from my deck!

V0420_39_00_01_0.text:
What!?
How unlucky can I get!

V0420_08_00_29_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Cross Counter!

V0420_09_00_00_0.text: Star Cestus uses an Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0420_09_00_01_0.text: Comet Cestus's effect activates when it destroys a monster!

V0420_09_00_02_0.text: I remove 1 Chaos Overlay Unit to use Comet Cestus's effect!

V0420_09_00_03_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Lion Heart's effect!

V0420_09_00_05_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Rhapsody in Berserk's effect!

V0420_09_00_06_0.text: Rhapsody in Berserk activates its effect!

V0420_09_00_07_0.text: Requiem in Berserk activates its effect!

V0420_09_00_08_0.text: I use 1 Chaos Overlay Unit to activate Requiem's effect!

V0420_09_00_10_0.text: Nova Kaiser's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0420_09_00_11_0.text: When Lead Yoke loses Overlay Units, it gets stronger!

V0420_09_00_12_0.text: I use 2 Overlay Units to play Cheat Commissioner's effect!

V0420_09_00_13_0.text: Glassjaw's effect activates when it's targeted for attack!

V0420_09_00_14_0.text: Glassjaw's effect activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0420_09_00_15_0.text: I activate Battlin' Boxer Shadow's effect from my hand!

V0420_09_00_16_0.text: Switchitter's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0420_09_00_17_0.text: Since I took damage, Battlin' Boxer Veil's effect activates!

V0420_09_00_18_0.text: Headgeared's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0420_09_00_21_0.text: I activate Battlin' Boxer Rib Gardna's effect!

V0420_09_00_23_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Ronin Raccoon's effect!

V0420_13_00_00_0.text: Step into the ring, Number 105: Battlin' Boxer Star Cestus!

V0420_37_00_00_0.text: Uncontrollable energy will throw the universe into disarray!

V0420_37_00_00_1.text:
Chaos Xyz Evolution!
Show yourself, Number C105!

V0420_37_00_01_0.text: From the outer realms of the unknown comes Number C105!

V0420_37_00_03_0.text:
The armor that binds the raging spirit!
Go, Number 80!

V0420_37_00_04_0.text:
Rise up, Number C80!
The melody that quiets the soul!

V0420_13_00_06_0.text: Appear, Number 79: Battlin' Boxer Nova Kaiser!

V0420_37_00_05_0.text: The fire in his soul sets his fist aflame!

V0420_37_00_06_0.text: He has the sway to get any outcome he wants!

V0420_13_00_19_0.text:
Show yourself!
Number 64: Ronin Raccoon Sandayu!

V0420_13_00_20_0.text: I Special Summon a Kagemusha Raccoon Token!

V0420_19_00_13_0.text: Show 'em why you're the champ, Headgeared!
